data.description:
This Modern Italian Villa is located on the secluded street of Olde Plantation Place in Kelly Plantation is perfect for a large family that loves to entertain.  This home boasts 6-bedrooms,  5-full and 2-half baths.  Approaching the home, you will be greeted by numerous Bevolo copper gas lanterns and monumental white columns.  Upon entry, the 20'+ trayed ceilings, floating staircase and breezeway set the ambiance of the home.  The first floor features an open dining area, large family room and  wet bar, along with a television and fireplace finished with white brick Nepal stone.  The large kitchen is a chef's delight featuring an oversize island, dual Subzero refrigerator/freezer, Wolf range, prep sinks and a casual dining area overlooking the pool lanai. The master suite features his and hers closets along with a spacious master bath complete with Kohler Hydromassage soaking tub, large multi-function shower, double vanities, heater floors and private washer and dryer. Automated window coverings are featured for each of the master windows and the door leading to the pool lanai.  On the opposing side of the first living level you will find a complete guest suite along with another guest bedroom and half bath.  The second floor features (3) guest bedrooms, playroom, secondary laundry room, conditioned storage area and a private office that could be used as a 6th bedroom. 

The pool lanai area features a large estate sized heated swimming pool complete with hot tub, elevated natural gas fire pit, complete outdoor kitchen along with TV and a full screened enclosure.   

Buyers can relax and enjoy the creature comforts provided by the natural gas Rinnai tankless hot water heaters, pool heater and the Generac Emergency generator that is always on standby to serve a portion of the home.  An electric fence for the front and rear of the home is also included for the pet lovers. Buyer to verify all dimensions.
